equals(Subformula, Subformula) - Static method in class nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.lib.FormulaComp
verifies whether two Subformulas are equal, meaning that they have equal
negations, and equal connectives and subformulas.
EQUIV - Static variable in class nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.lib.Chars
 
etaReduce(Subformula, Subformula, int) - Method in class nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.prover.SAKE
used by etaReductions() for subformula analysis
etaReductions() - Method in class nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.prover.SAKE
tries to find possible eta reductions in the current formula.
Uses the method etaReduce(Subformula subformula, int type) for the hard work.

The following formulas are applicable to eta reductions:
(0) p & -(p
(1) q & -(p
(2) -p & -(p
(3) -q & -(p
(4) p & p
(5) q & p
(6) -p & p
(7) -q & p
exists(Subformula) - Method in class nl.marcvanzee.KEProver.formula.Formula
verifies whether the Subformula exists in this formula
